~ about_clinic
Quartermaster Theta: This is a clinic. I install augments, swap out limbs, and keep people running. No questions, no records, no refunds.
Quartermaster Theta: If you need work done, browse my stock and pick what fits your budget. Or your body. Preferably both.
- What do you sell?
	=> about_stock
- Thanks.
	=> END

~ about_stock
Quartermaster Theta: Optics, subdermal plating, synthetic limbs, neural boosters — the usual. Everything I sell is tested and functional. Mostly.
Quartermaster Theta: If you're broke, the street vendor in Market Row has cheaper scrap. But you get what you pay for.
- Got it. Thanks.
	=> END
